Encapsulation: Binding code and data together in single unit.can be achived by access modifier.

Inheritance: Inheritance means acquries properties from one class to onother class.

Polymorphism: refers to the ability of class to perform different implementation of method,depending on type of object that passed to it.

Abstraction:hiding the implementation and showing functionality to user.



